com.interpss.simu.multicase.modify

Interface BusLoadCodeChange

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusLoadCodeChangeImpl

    public interface BusLoadCodeChange
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Bus Load Code Change'. Class for defining bus load code change

    The following features are supported:

    • To Code
    • Exp Load P
    • Exp Load Q
    See Also:
    MCaseModifyPackage.getBusLoadCodeChange()
